okedexBySearch(match.traduction.toLowerCase())\"\n            >\n              {{ match.traduction.toLowerCase() }}\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <button type=\"submit\" class=\"button\">\n          <img src=\"../assets/search.png\" alt=\"search-icon\" />\n        </button>\n      </form>\n      <button class=\"button all-btn\" @click=\"all\">Tous les Pokemons</button>\n    </section>\n    <section class=\"section pokedex-results\">\n      <ul class=\"results\">\n        <li v-for=\"(pokemon, index) in pokemons\" :key=\"index\">\n          <PokeCard :pokemon=\"pokemon\"></PokeCard>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n    </section>\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<script setup>\nimport { ref, toRefs, onUnmounted, onMounted, watch } from \"vue\";\nimport { useStore } from \"vuex\";\nimport PokeCard from \"../components/PokeCard.vue\";\n\nconst searchTerm = ref(\"\");\nconst timer = ref(null);\nconst store = useStore();\n// const pokemons = ref(store.state.pokemons);\nconst matchs = ref(store.state.matchs);\n\nconst pokemons = toRefs(store.state.pokemons);\n// watchs\n// watch(\n//   () => store.state.pokemons,\n//   () => {\n//     console.log(store.state.pokemons);\n//     pokemons.value = store.state.pokemons;\n//   }\n// );\nwatch(\n  () => store.state.matchs,\n  () => {\n    matchs.value = store.state.matchs;\n  }\n);\nwatch(searchTerm, (name) => {\n  if (timer.value) {\n    clearTimeout(timer);\n    timer.value = null;\n  }\n  timer.value = setTimeout(async () => {\n    await store.dispatch(\"generateMatchsPokemons\", name);\n  }, 255);\n});\n\n// functions\nasync function generateMorePokemons() {\n  if (window.scrollY >= window.scrollMaxY) {\n    await store.dispatch(\"generatePokedex\", false);\n  }\n}\nfunction generatePokedexBySearch(name) {\n  searchTerm.value = name;\n  const evt = new CustomEvent(\"submit\", { bubbles: true, cancelable: true });\n  document.getElementById(\"form\").dispatchEvent(evt);\n}\nasync function onSubmit(event) {\n  event.preventDefault();\n  if (searchTerm.value === \"\") {\n    window.addEventListener(\"scroll\", generateMorePokemons);\n  } else {\n    window.removeEventListener(\"scroll\", generateMorePokemons);\n  }\n  await store.dispatch(\"generatePokedexBySearch\", searchTerm.value);\n}\nasync function all() {\n  await store.dispatch(\"generatePokedex\", true);\n  window.addEventListener(\"scroll\", generateMorePokemons);\n}\n\n// lifeCyle\nonMounted(async () => {\n  await store.dispatch(\"generatePokedex\", true);\n  window.addEventListener(\"scroll\", generateMorePokemons);\n});\nonUnmounted(() => {\n  window.removeEventListener(\"scroll\", generateMorePokemons);\n});\n</script>\n\n<style scoped>\n.all-btn {\n  height: 50px;\n  font-size: 16px;\n  padding: 1em;\n  color: #fff;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  margin-left: 6em !important;\n}\n.button {\n  margin-left: 0.5em;\n  border-radius: 5px;\n  border: none;\n  background-color: #ff1a1a;\n  cursor: pointer;\n}\n.pokedex {\n  max-width: 1280px;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n}\n.section {\n  padding-top: 2em;\n  padding-bottom: 2em;\n  color: #fff;\n}\n.pokedex-header,\n.pokedex-filter {\n  padding-right: 3em;\n  padding-left: 3em;\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: flex-start;\n  align-items: flex-end;\n}\n.pokedex-header h1 {\n  font-size: 3em;\n  font-weight: 600;\n}\n.pokedex-filter form {\n  position: relative;\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: flex-end;\n}\n.pokedex-filter form div {\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  position: relative;\n}\n.pokedex-filter form div label {\n  margin-bottom: 0.8em;\n  font-size: 24px;\n}\ninput[type=\"text\"] {\n  height: 50px;\n  width: 100%;\n  min-width: 300px;\n  background-color: #ebebeb;\n  border: none;\n  border-radius: 5px;\n  padding: 1em;\n  line-height: 1.5;\n}\ninput[type=\"text\"]::placeholder {\n  color: #6d6d6d;\n  font-size: 16px;\n}\ninput[type=\"text\"]:focus-visible {\n  outline: auto;\n}\nbutton[type=\"submit\"] {\n  width: 50px;\n  height: 50px;\n}\nbutton[type=\"submit\"] img {\n  width: 24px;\n  transform: translateY(2px);\n}\n.matchs {\n  position: absolute !important;\n  background-color: #ebebeb;\n  top: 100%;\n  right: 0;\n  left: 0;\n  z-index: 1;\n}\n.matchs div {\n  box-sizing: content-box;\n  height: 100%;\n  color: #000;\n  padding: 1em;\n  cursor: pointer;\n}\n.matchs div:hover {\n  background-color: #ff1a1a;\n}\n.pokedex-results .results {\n  list-style: none;\n  display: flex;\n  flex-wrap: wrap;\n  justify-content: center;\n}\n.pokedex-results .results li {\n  margin: 0.8em;\n}\n</style>\n"]},"metadata":{},"sourceType":"module","externalDependencies":[]}